text:
Simple hash, 128-bit mixing function is just:<p><pre><code>  mix(const int A)
    {
      const int B = A+1;

      ds[A] *= P;
      ds[A] = rot(ds[A], 23);
      ds[A] *= Q;

      ds[B] ^= ds[A];

      ds[B] *= P;
      ds[B] = rot(ds[B], 23);
      ds[B] *= Q;
    }
</code></pre>
with P and Q prime.
